es White）是来自纽芬兰圣约翰斯的加拿大电影和电视演员。","name":"珀西·海因斯·怀特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"פרסי היינס וייט","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Персі Гайнс Вайт","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"波西·海恩斯·懷特（Percy Hynes White）是來自紐芬蘭聖約翰斯的加拿大電影和電視演員。","name":"波西·海恩斯·懷特","primary":false}}]}},"person_2433584_translations":{"at":1773688734880,"data":{"id":2433584,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tania Lentini","primary":true}}]}},"person_93331_translations":{"at":1773688737169,"data":{"id":93331,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дмитрий Назаров","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dmitri Nazarov","primary":false}}]}},"person_2982907_translations":{"at":1773688737772,"data":{"id":2982907,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zakhar Vykvytke","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zakhar Vykvytke","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1259506_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773689204206,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1259506,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"tl","original_title":"Last Shift","overview":"","popularity":0.0743,"poster_path":"/upwmUGTDBzVUAxjybPxeYQsnsnF.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2024-03-15","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Last Shift","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}},"person_552683_translations":{"at":1773689207629,"data":{"id":552683,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Hochu Otsuka (大塚 芳忠, Ōtsuka Hōchū, born Yoshitada Ōtsuka [same kanji], May 19, 1954) is a Japanese voice actor and narrator affiliated with the talent management firm Crazy Box.\n\nHe is best known for his roles as the voices of Kyao Mirao in Heavy Metal L-Gaim; Yazan Gable in Mobile Suit Zeta Gundam; Akira Sendō in Slam Dunk; SignalMan in Gekisou Sentai Carranger; Imagin, Deneb in Kamen Rider Den-O, Abuto in Gintama, Makoto Sōda in Captain Tsubasa and Jiraiya in Naruto. He is also the famous official dubbing roles for Jean-Claude Van Damme, Donnie Yen (especially in Ip Man series), Jeff Goldblum, Ray Liotta, Tim Robbins, John C. McGinley, Brent Spiner, Kiefer Sutherland, Robert Patrick and many more.","name":"Hochu Otsuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"大冢芳忠是日本资深男性声优、演员、剧情旁述，1954年5月19日出生于日本冈山县，冈山县出身，现所属于Crazy Box。\n\n音质浑厚低沉而不失中气，极具成熟魅力，无论是出演阴险狡诈狂傲不羁的恶役、滑稽搞怪的可笑角色还是忠厚淳朴型的豪爽阳光的青年男性类角色都能游刃有余。","name":"大冢芳忠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"오오츠카 호츄","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"大塚芳忠是日本的男性聲優、演員 。出身於岡山縣津山市，所屬公司為 Crazy Box。","name":"大塚芳忠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"大塚芳忠","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hochu Otsuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hochu Otsuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Хотю Оцука","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hóčú Ócuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hōchū Ōtsuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hōchū Ōtsuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"โฮจู โอตสึกะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hochu Otsuka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"大塚芳忠是日本資深男性聲優、演員、劇情旁述，1954 年 5 月 19 日出生於日本岡山縣，岡山縣出身，現所屬於 Crazy Box。\n\n音質渾厚低沉而不失中氣，極具成熟魅力，無論是出演陰險狡詐狂傲不羈的惡役、滑稽搞怪的可笑角色還是忠厚淳樸型的豪爽陽光的青年男性類角色都能遊刃有餘。","name":"大塚芳忠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Хочю Оцука","primary":false}}]}},"person_115150_translations":{"at":1773689208584,"data":{"id":115150,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kaya Rose Scodelario-Davis (née Humphrey; born 13 March 1992) is an English actress best known for her roles as Effy Stonem on the E4 teen drama Skins (2007–2010, 2013), and Teresa in the Maze Runner film series (2014–2018). Other roles include Catherine Earnshaw in Andrea Arnold's Wuthering Heights (2011), Carina Smyth in Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales (2017), Carole Ann Boone in Extremely Wicked, Shockingly Evil and Vile (2019), Haley Keller in Crawl (2019), Katarina Baker in the Netflix original series Spinning Out (2020) and Claire Redfield in Resident Evil: Welcome to Raccoon City (2021).","name":"Kaya Scodelario","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Kaya Rose Scodelario, nascida Kaya Rose Humphrey é uma atriz britânica conhecida pelo papel de Effy Stonem na série inglesa ''Skins'' e como Teresa no filme ''Maze Runner: Correr ou Morrer'' (2014).\n\nAlém de sucessos como ''Fúria de Titãs'' (2010); Maze Runner: Prova de Fogo (2015); é já está confirmada na sequência de ''Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales'', previsto para 2017.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"카야 스코델라리오","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Eine englische Schauspielerin (geboren am 13. März 1992). Sie ist vor allem bekannt für ihre Rollen als Effy Stonem auf dem E4 Teenagerdrama Skins (2007-2010; 2012), Catherine Earnshaw in Andrea Arnold's Wuthering Heights (2011), Teresa Agnes in der Maze Runner Filmreihe und Carina Smyth in Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales (2017).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kaya Rose Humphrey Scodelario (13 de marzo de 1992), más conocida como Kaya Scodelario, es una actriz británica de ascendencia italo-brasileña e inglesa.  Entre sus papeles, destacan el de Effy Stonem en la serie británica, Skins, Teresa Agnes en la trilogía de películas, Maze Runner, Kat Baker en la serie de Netflix, Spinning Out, y Carina Smyth en la película Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"Kaya Scodelario-Davis[1] (doğum adı Kaya Rose Humphrey; 13 Mart 1992) İngiliz aktris ve model. E4 kanalında yayınlanan Skins dizisindeki Effy Stonem rolü ile tanınır. The Maze Runner filmindeki Teresa Agnes rolü ise üstlendiği önemli bir roldür.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Kaya Rose Scodelario-Davis (ur. jako Kaya Rose Humphrey 13 marca 1992 w Haywards Heath) – brytyjska aktorka i modelka. Występowała m.in. w serialu Kumple i filmie Piraci z Karaibów: Zemsta Salazara.\n\nScodelario biegle mówi po portugalsku, jej ojciec jest Anglikiem, a matka Brazylijką. Jej rodzice rozwiedli się i Scodelario była wychowywana przez matkę, po czym przyjęła jej nazwisko. We wczesnym dzieciństwie była prześladowana, przez co miała niskie poczucie wartości, więc ucieczką przed rzeczywistością stał się teatr. Sławę zyskała dzięki roli Effy Stonem w serialu Kumple.\n\nOd 2015 roku żona Benjamina Walkera.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Кая Роуз Хамфри Скоделарио. Родилась в 1992-ом году в Лондоне, Великобритания. Была единственным ребёнком в семье. Отец работал в сфере транспорта, а мать была переводчицей. Училась в школе Ислингтон Артс. Работает актрисой и моделью. Была замужем за актёром Бенджамином Уокером, у пары 2-ое детей: сын и дочь. Свою текущую личную жизнь предпочитает держать в тайне\n\n🏆Главные награды🏆: BAFTA (2009) [Молокососы], Teen Choice Awards (2015) [Бегущий в лабиринте]\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Молокососы» (2007), «Бегущий в лабиринте» (2014), «Пираты Карибского моря» (2017), «Капкан» (2019)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: В детстве Кая страдала от буллинга из-за акцента и стеснительности","name":"Кая Скоделарио","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kaya Rose Humphrey Scodelario (13 de marzo de 1992), más conocida como Kaya Scodelario, es una actriz británica de ascendencia italo-brasileña e inglesa. Entre sus papeles, destacan el de Effy Stonem en la serie británica, Skins, Teresa Agnes en la trilogía de películas, Maze Runner, Kat Baker en la serie de Netflix, Spinning Out, y Carina Smyth en la película Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Η Κάγια Σκοντελάριο (Kaya Scodelario) είναι Βρετανίδα ηθοποιός. Πρωταγωνίστησε για πρώτη φορά στην κωμωδία Skins, του E4's (2007–2010, 2013), λαμβάνοντας δύο υποψηφιότητες για Χρυσή Νύμφη για την ερμηνεία της στον ρόλο της Έφυ Στόνεμ. Στη συνέχεια ανέλαβε πρωταγωνιστικούς ρόλους σε διάφορες ταινίες, όπως το Wuthering Heights (2011), η σειρά Maze Runner (2014–2018), οι Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales (2017), Crawl (2019) και Resident Evil: Welcome to Raccoon City (2021). Το 2024, πρωταγωνίστησε στην κωμική σειρά δράσης The Gentlemen και στην βιογραφική δραματική σειρά Senna, όπου μίλησε κάποιους διαλόγους στα πορτογαλικά.","name":"Κάγια Σκοντελάριο","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"卡雅·斯考达里奥，英国女演员，有着一幅成熟的外表，并且非常上镜。 凭借备受争议的热门青春剧《皮囊》成名 饰Effy Stonem，卡雅扮演主人公托尼（尼古拉斯·霍尔特）的妹妹。 与她阴郁的思想和行为相比，我们的孩子无论怎样都能称得上乖巧。她是Tony的妹妹，她是Tony真正关心的人，但她却总是带来Tony不想看到的结果。 2008年她还出演了大卫·鲍伊之子邓肯·琼斯的长片处女作《月球》，扮演山姆·洛克威尔的女儿。","name":"卡雅·斯考达里奥","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"カヤ・スコデラリオ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"凱亞・絲柯黛蘭莉歐","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кая Скоделаріо","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"קאיה סקודלריו","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"卡雅·斯考達里奧，英國女演員，有著一幅成熟的外表，並且非常上鏡。\n\n憑藉備受爭議的熱門青春劇《皮囊》成名 飾 Effy Stonem，卡雅扮演主人公託尼（尼古拉斯·霍爾特）的妹妹。\n\n與她陰鬱的思想和行為相比，我們的孩子無論怎樣都能稱得上乖巧。她是 Tony 的妹妹，她是 Tony 真正關心的人，但她卻總是帶來 Tony 不想看到的結果。\n\n2008 年她還出演了大衞·鮑伊之子鄧肯·瓊斯的長片處女作《The Moon: 緊急營救》，扮演山姆·洛克威爾的女兒。","name":"卡雅·斯考達里奧","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1576751_credits":{"at":1773689209804,"data":{"id":1576751,"cast":[],"crew":[]}},"person_3221238_translations":{"at":1773689210422,"data":{"id":3221238,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kim Mu Jun is a South Korean actor.\n\nHe made his acting debut in the 2020 drama \"It's Okay to be Sensitive\" (좀 예민해도 괜찮아) and signed a contract with 9ato Entertainment (9아토엔터테인먼트) that same year.","name":"Kim Moo-joon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金茂俊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金茂俊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"김무준","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金茂俊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kim Moo-joon","primary":false}}]}},"tv_244244_keywords":{"at":1773689213610,"data":{"id":244244,"results":[{"name":"based on novel or book","id":818},{"name":"drug addiction","id":1803},{"name":"daughter","id":5600},{"name":"miniseries","id